@startuml
title DORA Metrics Automation Tool - Deployment and Control Flow

actor "DevOps User" as User
participant "Gin API\nRouter" as API
participant "Handler\nLayer" as Handler
participant "Service\nLayer" as Service
participant "DAO\nLayer" as DAO
participant "MongoDB" as DB
participant "GitLab\nConnector" as GitLab
participant "Prometheus\nConnector" as Prometheus
participant "Metrics\nCalculation" as Metrics
participant "Prometheus\nMonitoring" as PromServer

== Integration Setup ==
User -> API: POST /integrations\n(GitLab config)
activate API
API -> Handler: createIntegration()
activate Handler
Handler -> Service: validateAndStoreIntegration()
activate Service
Service -> DAO: saveIntegration()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: insert(integration)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: success
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: integrationId
deactivate DAO
Service --> Handler: integrationId
deactivate Service
Handler --> API: 201 Created
deactivate Handler
API --> User: integrationId
deactivate API

== Dataflow Configuration ==
User -> API: POST /dataflows\n(repo, metrics config)
activate API
API -> Handler: createDataflow()
activate Handler
Handler -> Service: setupDataflow()
activate Service
Service -> DAO: saveDataflow()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: insert(dataflow)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: dataflowId
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: dataflowId
deactivate DAO
Service --> Handler: dataflowId
deactivate Service
Handler --> API: 201 Created
deactivate Handler
API --> User: dataflowId
deactivate API

== Data Collection and Metrics Calculation ==
Service -> Service: scheduledJob()
activate Service
Service -> GitLab: fetchOrganizations()
activate GitLab
GitLab -> GitLab: authenticateWithToken()
GitLab --> Service: organizations
deactivate GitLab

Service -> GitLab: fetchRepositories()
activate GitLab
GitLab --> Service: repositories
deactivate GitLab

Service -> GitLab: fetchPullRequests()
activate GitLab
GitLab --> Service: pullRequests
deactivate GitLab

Service -> GitLab: fetchCommits()
activate GitLab
GitLab --> Service: commits
deactivate GitLab

Service -> GitLab: fetchPipelineRuns()
activate GitLab
GitLab --> Service: pipelineRuns
deactivate GitLab

Service -> DAO: saveBulkData(commits,\npipelines, repos)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: bulkInsert()
activate DB
DB --> DAO: success
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: saved
deactivate DAO

Service -> Metrics: aggregateDailyData()
activate Metrics
Metrics -> DAO: fetchRawData()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: query(commits,\npipelines, date)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: rawData
deactivate DB
DAO --> Metrics: rawData
deactivate DAO

Metrics -> Metrics: calculateDeploymentFrequency()
Metrics -> Metrics: calculateLeadTime()

Metrics -> DAO: saveDailySummary()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: insert(dailyMetrics)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: success
deactivate DB
DAO --> Metrics: saved
deactivate DAO
Metrics --> Service: aggregationComplete
deactivate Metrics
deactivate Service

== Prometheus Alert Handling ==
PromServer -> API: POST /alerts\n(alert webhook)
activate API
API -> Handler: handleAlert()
activate Handler
Handler -> Service: processAlert()
activate Service
Service -> DAO: createIncident()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: insert(incident)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: incidentId
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: incidentId
deactivate DAO

Service -> Metrics: calculateMTTR()
activate Metrics
Metrics -> DAO: fetchIncidents()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: query(incidents, resolved)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: incidents
deactivate DB
DAO --> Metrics: incidents
deactivate DAO

Metrics -> Metrics: computeMeanTimeToRestore()

Metrics -> DAO: updateMTTRMetric()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: update(mttrMetric)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: success
deactivate DB
DAO --> Metrics: updated
deactivate DAO
Metrics --> Service: mttrCalculated
deactivate Metrics

Service --> Handler: alertProcessed
deactivate Service
Handler --> API: 200 OK
deactivate Handler
API --> PromServer: acknowledged
deactivate API

== Metrics Retrieval ==
User -> API: GET /metrics/dora\n?dataflowId=X
activate API
API -> Handler: getMetrics()
activate Handler
Handler -> Service: retrieveMetrics()
activate Service
Service -> Metrics: calculateChangeFailureRate()
activate Metrics
Metrics -> DAO: fetchPipelines(failed)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: query(pipelines, status)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: pipelineData
deactivate DB
DAO --> Metrics: pipelineData
deactivate DAO

Metrics -> Metrics: computeChangeFailureRate()
Metrics --> Service: changeFailureRate
deactivate Metrics

Service -> DAO: getAggregatedMetrics()
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: query(metrics, dataflowId)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: metricsData
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: metricsData
deactivate DAO

Service --> Handler: doraMetrics
deactivate Service
Handler --> API: 200 OK + metrics JSON
deactivate Handler
API --> User: DORA metrics response
deactivate API

== Metrics Export to Prometheus ==
PromServer -> API: GET /metrics
activate API
API -> API: collectPrometheusMetrics()
API --> PromServer: metrics in\nPrometheus format
deactivate API

@enduml
